### ============================================
### Approval Workflow API Tests
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = 
@tenantId = 

### ============================================
### 1. APPROVAL FLOWS - 流程定义管理
### ============================================

### 1.1 创建流程定义
POST {{baseUrl}}/approval/flows
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "请假审批流程",
  "definitionJson": "{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":\"start\",\"type\":\"start\",\"data\":{\"label\":\"开始\"}},{\"id\":\"approve1\",\"type\":\"approve\",\"data\":{\"label\":\"部门主管审批\",\"assigneeType\":\"DepartmentLeader\",\"assigneeValue\":\"1\"}},{\"id\":\"approve2\",\"type\":\"approve\",\"data\":{\"label\":\"人力审批\",\"assigneeType\":\"Role\",\"assigneeValue\":\"HR\"}},{\"id\":\"end\",\"type\":\"end\",\"data\":{\"label\":\"结束\"}}],\"edges\":[{\"id\":\"e1\",\"source\":\"start\",\"target\":\"approve1\"},{\"id\":\"e2\",\"source\":\"approve1\",\"target\":\"approve2\"},{\"id\":\"e3\",\"source\":\"approve2\",\"target\":\"end\"}]}"
}

### 1.2 获取流程定义列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/approval/flows?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&status=Draft
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 1.3 获取流程定义详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/approval/flows/{flowId}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 1.4 更新流程定义（仅草稿可编辑）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/approval/flows/{flowId}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "请假审批流程v2",
  "definitionJson": "{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":\"start\",\"type\":\"start\",\"data\":{\"label\":\"开始\"}},{\"id\":\"approve1\",\"type\":\"approve\",\"data\":{\"label\":\"部门主管审批\",\"assigneeType\":\"DepartmentLeader\",\"assigneeValue\":\"1\"}},{\"id\":\"end\",\"type\":\"end\",\"data\":{\"label\":\"结束\"}}],\"edges\":[{\"id\":\"e1\",\"source\":\"start\",\"target\":\"approve1\"},{\"id\":\"e2\",\"source\":\"approve1\",\"target\":\"end\"}]}"
}

### 1.5 发布流程定义
POST {{baseUrl}}/approval/flows/{flowId}/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 1.6 禁用流程定义
POST {{baseUrl}}/approval/flows/{flowId}/disable
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 1.7 删除流程定义（仅草稿可删除）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/approval/flows/{flowId}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ============================================
### 2. APPROVAL RUNTIME - 流程运行时管理
### ============================================

### 2.1 发起流程实例
POST {{baseUrl}}/approval/runtime/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "definitionId": 1,
  "businessKey": "leave-request-001",
  "dataJson": "{\"leaveType\":\"sick\",\"startDate\":\"2026-02-01\",\"endDate\":\"2026-02-03\",\"reason\":\"感冒\"}"
}

### 2.2 获取我发起的流程实例
GET {{baseUrl}}/approval/runtime/my-instances?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&status=Running
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 2.3 获取流程实例详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/approval/runtime/instances/{instanceId}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 2.4 获取流程实例历史事件
GET {{baseUrl}}/approval/runtime/instances/{instanceId}/history?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 2.5 取消流程实例
POST {{baseUrl}}/approval/runtime/instances/{instanceId}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 2.6 撤回流程（发起人撤回）
POST {{baseUrl}}/approval/runtime/instances/{instanceId}/operations?taskId={taskId}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operationType": 29,
  "comment": "撤回流程"
}

### 2.7 转办任务
POST {{baseUrl}}/approval/runtime/instances/{instanceId}/operations?taskId={taskId}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operationType": 21,
  "targetAssigneeValue": "200",
  "comment": "转办给其他处理人"
}

### 2.8 加签
POST {{baseUrl}}/approval/runtime/instances/{instanceId}/operations?taskId={taskId}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operationType": 25,
  "additionalAssigneeValues": ["300", "301"],
  "comment": "加签审批人"
}

### 2.9 打回修改
POST {{baseUrl}}/approval/runtime/instances/{instanceId}/operations?taskId={taskId}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operationType": 18,
  "comment": "打回修改，请补充材料"
}

### 2.10 退回任意节点
POST {{baseUrl}}/approval/runtime/instances/{instanceId}/operations?taskId={taskId}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operationType": 23,
  "targetNodeId": "approve1",
  "comment": "退回至第一个审批节点"
}

### 2.11 撤销同意
POST {{baseUrl}}/approval/runtime/instances/{instanceId}/operations?taskId={taskId}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operationType": 32,
  "comment": "撤销之前的同意"
}

### ============================================
### 3. APPROVAL TASKS - 审批任务管理
### ============================================

### 3.1 获取我的待办任务
GET {{baseUrl}}/approval/tasks/my-tasks?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&status=Pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 3.2 获取实例内的所有任务
GET {{baseUrl}}/approval/tasks/by-instance/{instanceId}?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 3.3 同意审批任务
POST {{baseUrl}}/approval/tasks/{taskId}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comment": "同意，符合请假规范"
}

### 3.4 驳回审批任务
POST {{baseUrl}}/approval/tasks/{taskId}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comment": "不同意，请假天数过长"
}

### ============================================
### 4. APPROVAL DEPARTMENT LEADERS - 部门负责人管理
### ============================================

### 4.1 设置部门负责人
POST {{baseUrl}}/approval/department-leaders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "departmentId": 1,
  "leaderUserId": 100
}

### 4.2 获取部门负责人
GET {{baseUrl}}/approval/department-leaders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 4.3 移除部门负责人
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/approval/department-leaders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ============================================
### 5. APPROVAL COPY RECORDS - 抄送记录管理
### ============================================

### 5.1 获取我的抄送记录（全部）
GET {{baseUrl}}/approval/copy-records/my-copies?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 5.2 获取我的抄送记录（仅未读）
GET {{baseUrl}}/approval/copy-records/my-copies?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&isRead=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 5.3 获取我的抄送记录（仅已读）
GET {{baseUrl}}/approval/copy-records/my-copies?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&isRead=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 5.4 标记抄送记录为已读
POST {{baseUrl}}/approval/copy-records/{copyRecordId}/mark-read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ============================================
### 5. APPROVAL COPY RECORDS - 抄送记录管理
### ============================================

### 5.1 获取我的抄送记录（全部）
GET {{baseUrl}}/approval/copy-records/my-copies?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 5.2 获取我的抄送记录（仅未读）
GET {{baseUrl}}/approval/copy-records/my-copies?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&isRead=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 5.3 获取我的抄送记录（仅已读）
GET {{baseUrl}}/approval/copy-records/my-copies?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&isRead=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 5.4 标记抄送记录为已读
POST {{baseUrl}}/approval/copy-records/{copyRecordId}/mark-read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
